Ok when i first tried to go into shops.cfg it siad something like "we cannot open this folder because we dont know the foundation or somethin" sorry i dont remember exactly what it said.

Now some of the folders when i click on them say's this
c:/Documents and Settings/Bill_2/Desktop/Allstar-Scape v2/drops.cfg The archive is either unknown format or damaged.
It says this with
Autospawn ~ Dialogues ~ drops ~ item ~ npc ~ npcdrops ~ shops ~ sun ~ Teleport ~ worldobject.
